  <brief_title>Surgicel速 Fibrillar for Delayed Bleeding After ESD</brief_title>
  <official_title>Surgicel速 (Fibrillar) for Preventing Delayed Bleeding After ESD in Stomach: A Prospective Randomized Study</official_title>
  <sponsors>
    <lead_sponsor>
      <agency>Soonchunhyang University Hospital</agency>
